{"tid":1568992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"查詢/投訴樊潔玲醫生 template","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T08:55:09.000Z","uid":61697,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"cf3689d5ea35489bde7d400fda8d6820d03ed65b","tid":1568992,"uid":61697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:42:46.000Z","msg":"隨便用 請自行修改<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nmchk@dh.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n執事先生你好：<br />\n<br />\n本人從網上得知，樊潔玲醫生於2019年9月14日被揭發，事前開出2019年9月16日之醫生診症收據，有偽造文件之嫌，請 貴局嚴肅調查此事。醫生之醫德醫品極為重要，絕不容許任何做假。如 貴局發現當中有任何違規之行為，請採取適當行動嚴懲。<br />\n<br />\n現附上有關之網絡連結<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2449419911793357?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F279926822076021%2Fposts%2F2449419911793357%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=33d8a570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2449419911793357?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n香港市民<br />\nXXX"},{"pid":"f17b97d5b06f3e219a3b8c98923647901f5088bb","tid":1568992,"uid":288765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"一句愛國，一句撐警，可保平安。肯定好似葉苦事件咁不了了之。"},{"pid":"3d65f5ee17a1384a9c90fdf21f8a1a05839346ff","tid":1568992,"uid":61697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:47:39.000Z","msg":"915<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d00b493822d91ab9929f2d6ac668226b5c6bc0","tid":1568992,"uid":194767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:48:56.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef1bd1bbcfddc106a9df5d09c974080b8d6ecc7","tid":1568992,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0